Sound of the Sea;;2001;;R;;Drama,Romance;;6.0;;Bigas Luna;;Jordi Mollà,Leonor Watling,Eduard Fernández,Neus Agulló,Pep Cortés,Ricky Colomer,Sergio Caballero,Carla Collado,Juan Muñoz,Pablo Rivero,Ana María Máñez,Clara Serrano,Bautista Devesa,José Gonga,Ricardo López,Javier Coromina,Ximo Vidal,Paco Bertomeu;;A new literature teacher, Ulises, comes to a small town near the sea and falls in love with a young woman, Martina. This woman is loved by a rich businessman named Alberto but chooses Ulises. Soon after their marriage and the birth of their son, Ulises vanishes while fishing at sea. In the meanwhile Martina marries Alberto, but all is not what it seems...;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0261311/